{"tid":47350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"古中國科技啟導歐洲文藝復興 達芬奇發明抄中國","createTime":"2016-12-20T09:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T07:40:27.000Z","uid":51546,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5c434c9de7aeef441aaedc517d54ffb414c0f37","tid":47350,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"備受爭議的英國業餘歷史學家孟席斯(Gavin Menzies)再推出新書，聲稱15世紀意大利文藝復興時期達芬奇(Leonardo da Vinci)的許多機器設計圖，與中國古代的機器「不尋常地」相似。他聲稱，一支中國船隊在1434年曾帶了一批中國科技典籍到意大利，為西方的工程和科技發展，以至整個文藝復興運動，奠下基礎。<br />\n<br />\n「中國船隊赴意啟導文藝復興」<br />\n<br />\n孟席斯是業餘歷史學家，2002年《1421:中國人發現美洲》一書曾指中國人比哥倫布早70年發現美洲新大陸。他今次出版新書《1434：一隊龐大的中國艦隊抵達意大利並燃點起文藝復興》(1434: The Year A Magnificent Chinese Fleet Sailed To Italy and Ignited The Renaissance)，認為當年一名中國特使從威尼斯前往佛羅倫斯，把一些科技典籍交給當時的教宗歐日納四世，結果啟導文藝復興。「我認為這些書正好燃點起文藝復興，達芬奇和伽里略建立的東西，正好是基於中國人的知識&hellip;&hellip;達芬奇基本上只是將所有(中國人的)東西，用立體方法呈現，同時並加以改良。」<br />\n<br />\n他稱一隊4艘船的中國遠征船隊當年抵達威尼斯，將比當時歐洲一切都要先進的百科全書、天文圖及地圖給歐洲人。「中國特使曾前往佛羅倫斯」的說法，是建基於他在哥倫布的書信中，發現一封意大利數學家托斯卡內利的信件，他聲稱信上寫覑﹕「教宗歐日納四世在位時，一名中國大使曾會見他。」<br />\n<br />\n比對中國古籍《農書》設計圖<br />\n<br />\n孟席斯又稱，達芬奇的設計概念其實是源自中國科技。齒輪、水車以及其他儀器的設計早就為中國典籍所載，被意大利人塔可拉及法蘭席斯科複製及修改，最後流到達芬奇手上。為證明其說法，孟席斯在書中印了幾幅中國《農書》等古籍的設計圖，將它們跟達芬奇、塔可拉及法蘭席斯科的設計圖並列。<br />\n<br />\n他聲稱，若見解獲得接納，歷史學家一直相信的「歐洲中心論」將會受到重大衝擊。研究達芬奇的牛津大學美術史教授肯普(Martin Kemp)，雖指孟席斯的說法「很有意思」，但強調必須進一步研究。他指出，「孟席斯說一些東西看上去相似，所以它是抄襲來的&hellip;&hellip;這論證方法並不夠有力」。一些西方學者更強烈質疑孟席斯的觀點，指他的書應被歸納入「虛構小說」，維基百科相關的英語網頁，亦作出強烈懷疑。"},{"pid":"840bfd640299e82c90dc012db404566a3ea531cd","tid":47350,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:38:40.000Z","msg":"等睇大支那膠精神自慰"},{"pid":"498b06646dae43771b938217448dd5147b013319","tid":47350,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:39:46.000Z","msg":"達文西係中國人黎"},{"pid":"5add7dae09927cedcea973f1acd708ef8d82ae69","tid":47350,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:41:30.000Z","msg":"有問題咩？自古以來，歐洲都係中國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係&hellip;係全世界都係中國，聽聞阿當同夏娃都係中國人黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb9e8d78410f7e8aeb5f21297e0605652ca5d51","tid":47350,"uid":32732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:43:03.000Z","msg":"聞西：中國特務來！ 有無睇零零柒"},{"pid":"dd7d07a0aa62ae6462cc17b9dfa466d86ee03278","tid":47350,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:47:12.000Z","msg":"聞西國家有任務比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50003b6a4a54f6cc94f235263fa6550fc4c17437","tid":47350,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:50:46.000Z","msg":"New Balance同新把撚都異常相似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4278b005e40d3f1324224ed5bfbdf83906cdd4af","tid":47350,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>New Balance同新把撚都異常相似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b701b50f410514dee2b99bcbad4b17a66d6d923","tid":47350,"uid":32650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:08:59.000Z","msg":"尼類文好小事啦<br />\n<br />\n最撚好笑係以前睇過一篇講拿破崙有本孫子兵法"},{"pid":"396525e7199ff324b9785d0a8d391933abcacefd","tid":47350,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:28:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尼類文好小事啦<br />\n<br />\n最撚好笑係以前睇過一篇講拿破崙有本孫子兵法</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拿法崙又係中國人?"},{"pid":"637e337ef07326d3c50144960bb362ee86140eee","tid":47350,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:49:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>尼類文好小事啦<br />\n<br />\n最撚好笑係以前睇過一篇講拿破崙有本孫子兵法</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拿法崙又係中國人?</blockquote><br />\n威靈頓都係中國人<br />\n即係中國人打中國人"},{"pid":"c8a7865e492711cdd076126673fdbdb8ea8974e2","tid":47350,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:54:27.000Z","msg":"睇錯芬達"},{"pid":"2429e6bceb93bbef50e4e4d2dc4a11e4a1f4d386","tid":47350,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>尼類文好小事啦<br />\n<br />\n最撚好笑係以前睇過一篇講拿破崙有本孫子兵法</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拿法崙又係中國人?</blockquote><br />\n威靈頓都係中國人<br />\n即係中國人打中國人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n歐獨可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白人背祖忘宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2b987f7807d01837602933c4f195f420f94a82","tid":47350,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:55:20.000Z","msg":"係又點？中國早就滅亡啦，而家係後清，黃俄，支那賤種。"},{"pid":"e40c28f21fc1dde4834b7b8e0047cba2b3dd8f2c","tid":47350,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:14:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係又點？中國早就滅亡啦，而家係後清，黃俄，支那賤種。</blockquote><br />\n本身中國就係賤種"},{"pid":"7a333f7be4582f6127f865fc6c17e68d42bac78b","tid":47350,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係又點？中國早就滅亡啦，而家係後清，黃俄，支那賤種。</blockquote><br />\n本身中國就係賤種</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non9 五毛死遠啲"},{"pid":"9418442641c2615f1d5071b5f812509ec797c9d8","tid":47350,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係又點？中國早就滅亡啦，而家係後清，黃俄，支那賤種。</blockquote><br />\n本身中國就係賤種</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non9 五毛死遠啲</blockquote><br />\n反中就係五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117bf32bab4a05cb21e4a792624cb21df37ff824","tid":47350,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>尼類文好小事啦<br />\n<br />\n最撚好笑係以前睇過一篇講拿破崙有本孫子兵法</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拿法崙又係中國人?</blockquote><br />\n拿破崙有孫子兵法其實有咩咁出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個陣中西已經交流左好耐"}]}